🏨 Hotel Menu Ordering System
This Python script simulates a simple hotel menu ordering system where users can order items from a predefined menu and calculate the total cost.

📋 Features
Displays a list of available items with their prices.

Allows users to order one or two items.

Verifies if the ordered item is available in the menu.

Calculates and displays the total amount to be paid.

📄 Menu Items
🍕 Pizza: 40 Rs

🍝 Pasta: 30 Rs

🍟 Fries: 30 Rs

🍔 Burger: 60 Rs

🥤 Coke: 40 Rs
